short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extract Beatport track URLs from a Crates.co crate

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Spinnin Beans™ Crates.co Track Extractor is a lightweight tool that simplifies the process of extracting track links from Crates.co playlists. With just one click, users can easily gather all track URLs from their Crates.co playlist and export them for seamless transfer to Soundiiz or other playlist management platforms.

Save Time: Instead of manually copying track links one by one, this app automates the extraction process, saving you valuable time.
Easy to Use: Designed with a user-friendly interface, it’s perfect for DJs, music enthusiasts, or anyone who needs a fast way to manage and export their track lists.
Perfect for Playlist Management: It integrates effortlessly with your Crates.co playlists, making it easy to transfer your favorite tracks across different platforms.
